data.description:
3-bedroom, 2-bathroom brick home with a bonus room.The home features a rocking chair front porch, an outdoor kitchen, and sits on almost an acre of land. Inside, there are beautiful hardwood flooring and wainscoting in the dining room, with 12'' ceilings. The study has French doors, and the kitchen is equipped with granite countertops, slate smudge-proof appliances, tile floors, and a built-in breakfast bar. The cabinets and pantry are upgraded.

The owner's suite boasts ceiling fans, tray ceilings, and walk-in closets. The home has a split floor plan with a large guest bathroom, double sinks, custom tile floors, and a transom window. The guest bedroom has a ceiling fan and walk-in closet. The bonus room features vaulted ceilings and could be used as a game room with a built-in bar, large enough for a pool table. The backyard is described as awesome and includes an outdoor kitchen. There's also a privacy fence with a double gate.
